446
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:20,060
Demon-hunting Crossbow!

447
00:42:23,520 --> 00:42:26,040
Fu Yu!

448
00:42:57,540 --> 00:42:59,380
Ye Qingyu!

449
00:43:29,300 --> 00:43:31,033
Ye Qingyu!

450
00:43:32,160 --> 00:43:34,093
Ye Qingyu!

