457
00:43:57,820 --> 00:44:00,600
This death is worth it.

458
00:44:00,600 --> 00:44:03,040
What are you talking about? You won't die.

459
00:44:03,040 --> 00:44:05,470
I won't let you die.

460
00:44:07,000 --> 00:44:08,633
Ye Qingyu.

461
00:44:09,300 --> 00:44:13,000
I thought I would never be as good as Jiang Rao.

462
00:44:13,000 --> 00:44:14,900
Because he's already dead.

463
00:44:14,900 --> 00:44:17,330
He'll live in your heart forever.

464
00:44:17,330 --> 00:44:20,520
I didn't expect that now I'm also...

465
00:44:21,700 --> 00:44:23,640
Ye Qingyu, you're not Jiang Rao.

466
00:44:23,640 --> 00:44:25,460
And don't even think about becoming Jiang Rao.

467
00:44:25,460 --> 00:44:27,640
You are Ye Qingyu.

468
00:44:28,230 --> 00:44:30,620
♫ <i>Ingenuine affection is also enough</i> ♫

469
00:44:30,620 --> 00:44:32,520
♫ <i>Sincerity makes flirtation hard</i> ♫

470
00:44:32,520 --> 00:44:34,350
Pianran,

471
00:44:35,480 --> 00:44:38,030
if only I could have met you

472
00:44:38,030 --> 00:44:39,873
earlier.

473
00:44:39,873 --> 00:44:45,180
♫ <i>Although fireworks are short-lived, they are easily enjoyed</i> ♫

474
00:44:45,180 --> 00:44:50,440
♫ <i>But this time, who will be the one</i> ♫

475
00:44:50,440 --> 00:44:53,030
So I could have fallen in love with you earlier.

476
00:44:53,030 --> 00:44:54,790
To dote on you.

477
00:44:59,020 --> 00:45:03,753
Pianran, demons live much longer than humans.

478
00:45:03,753 --> 00:45:05,860
Will you still remember me

479
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,940
after a few hundred years?

480
00:45:10,200 --> 00:45:12,190
You jerk!

481
00:45:12,190 --> 00:45:14,480
If you dare to die,

482
00:45:14,480 --> 00:45:17,470
I'll forget everything about you!

483
00:45:18,640 --> 00:45:20,700
Just forget about me.

484
00:45:21,900 --> 00:45:24,000
Don't feel sad for me.

485
00:45:25,020 --> 00:45:29,460
After living the best days of my life with you,

486
00:45:30,300 --> 00:45:32,570
there's nothing I regret...

487
00:45:32,570 --> 00:45:34,570
when I leave the world.

488
00:45:36,360 --> 00:45:38,293
What a shame.

489
00:45:39,940 --> 00:45:41,673
We...

490
00:45:42,880 --> 00:45:45,410
